# **UML COMPONENT DIAGRAM (Text‑Based)**

```
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                   Virtual Monitoring Center                   |
|---------------------------------------------------------------|
|  Interfaces:                                                  |
|    + registerAgent()                                          |
|    + assignMonitoringUnit()                                   |
|    + routeData()                                              |
|                                                               |
|  Components:                                                  |
|    - Data Ingestion Layer                                     |
|    - Monitoring Unit Manager                                  |
|    - Agent Workstation Manager                                |
|    - Organizational Hierarchy Manager                         |
+---------------------------+-----------------------------------+
                            |
                            | uses
                            v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                     Data Ingestion Layer                      |
|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Interfaces:                                                   |
|   + captureData()                                             |
|   + normalizeData()                                           |
|   + validateData()                                            |
|   + routeToMonitoringUnit()                                   |
+---------------------------+-----------------------------------+
                            |
                            | sends data to
                            v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                      Monitoring Unit (MU)                     |
|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Interfaces:                                                   |
|   + storeData()                                               |
|   + provideContext()                                          |
|   + updateThresholds()                                        |
|                                                               |
| Subcomponents:                                                |
|   - Data History Store                                        |
|   - Context Processor                                         |
+---------------------------+-----------------------------------+
                            |
                            | provides feed to
                            v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                   Virtual Workstation Component               |
|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Interfaces:                                                   |
|   + displayData()                                             |
|   + loadTools()                                               |
|   + sendMessage()                                             |
|                                                               |
| Subcomponents:                                                |
|   - Dashboard Renderer                                        |
|   - Toolset Loader                                            |
+---------------------------+-----------------------------------+
                            |
                            | used by
                            v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                   Virtual Software Agent (VSA)                |
|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Interfaces:                                                   |
|   + analyzeData()                                             |
|   + detectAnomaly()                                           |
|   + generateReport()                                          |
|   + escalate()                                                |
|   + updateRules()                                             |
|                                                               |
| Subcomponents:                                                |
|   - Knowledge Base                                            |
|   - Analytics Engine                                          |
|   - Anomaly Detector                                          |
+---------------------------+-----------------------------------+
                            |
                            | sends events to
                            v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                   Decision & Action Engine                    |
|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Interfaces:                                                   |
|   + evaluateEvent()                                           |
|   + generateAlert()                                           |
|   + recommendAction()                                         |
|                                                               |
| Subcomponents:                                                |
|   - Rule Engine                                               |
|   - Severity Model                                            |
+---------------------------+-----------------------------------+
                            |
                            | forwards to
                            v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                 Reporting & Escalation Component              |
|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Interfaces:                                                   |
|   + packageReport()                                           |
|   + routeToSupervisor()                                       |
|   + escalate()                                                |
|                                                               |
| Subcomponents:                                                |
|   - Routing Logic                                             |
|   - Alert Formatter                                           |
+---------------------------+-----------------------------------+
                            |
                            | notifies
                            v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                       Supervisory Agent                       |
|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Interfaces:                                                   |
|   + validateReport()                                          |
|   + provideFeedback()                                         |
|   + approveAction()                                           |
|   + submitInsight()                                           |
+---------------------------+-----------------------------------+
                            |
                            | updates
                            v
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
|                 Lessons-Learned Repository                    |
|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Interfaces:                                                   |
|   + storeInsight()                                            |
|   + updateRules()                                             |
|   + distributeUpdates()                                       |
|                                                               |
| Subcomponents:                                                |
|   - Insight Store                                             |
|   - Rule Update Manager                                       |
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
```

---

# **What This Component Diagram Shows**

- The system is composed of **modular components**, each with clear responsibilities.  
- Data flows from **Data Ingestion → Monitoring Unit → Workstation → VSA → Decision Engine → Reporting → Supervisory Agent → Lessons Learned**.  
- Each component exposes **interfaces** that define how other components interact with it.  
- The architecture supports **scalability, modularity, and continuous improvement**.

